quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  96,19,"Rárá (ọ̀rọ̀ kò rí bí ó ṣe ń sọ nípa Wa). Má ṣe tẹ̀lé tirẹ̀. Forí kanlẹ̀ (kí o kírun), kí o sì súnmọ́ (Allāhu)."
  100,7,"Dájúdájú Allāhu sì ń jẹ́ Ẹlẹ́rìí lórí ìyẹn."
  100,8,"Àti pé dájúdájú ènìyàn le gan-an níbi ìfẹ́ oore ayé."
  100,9,"Ṣé kò mọ̀ pé nígbà tí wọ́n bá tú ohun tó wà nínú sàréè jáde (fún àjíǹde),"
  101,4,"(Òhun ni) ọjọ́ tí ènìyàn yó dà bí àfòpiná tí wọ́n fọ́nká síta,"
  101,5,"àwọn àpáta yó sì dà bí ẹ̀gbọ̀n òwú tí wọ́n gbọ̀n dànù."
  101,6,"Nítorí náà, ní ti ẹni tí òṣùwọ̀n (iṣẹ́ rere) rẹ̀ bá tẹ̀wọ̀n,"
  102,1,"Wíwá oore ayé ní ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ fún ìyanràn ṣíṣe ti kó àìrójú fẹ́sìn ba yín"
  102,2,"títí ẹ fi wọ inú sàréè."
  102,3,"Rárá (kò yẹ kó rí bẹ́ẹ̀, àmọ́) láìpẹ́ ẹ máa mọ̀."